      "startTime": 8.0803854624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "どんどん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bom Bom",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0803854624,
      "endTime": 9.191156450900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3978231151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "パフパフ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honk Honk~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3978231151,
      "endTime": 11.4405215461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.640521558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、今日の議題は、どりきゅんに勝つために\n私達は何をすればいいかですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ today’s topic is what we should do\nto beat DoriKyun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.640521558,
      "endTime": 18.2498186589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスと合同練習することは決定していますが\nそれ以外にも出来ることはあるはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been decided that we’ll have joint practice with IIIX‚\nbut there must be other things we can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4272789955,
      "endTime": 25.0500001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2166682243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "でも対戦まで後二週間ほどしかないのよ？\n練習を頑張る他にやれることがあるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we only have about two weeks left before the match‚ right?\nIs there anything else we can do besides practice hard?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2166682243,
      "endTime": 34.2965774219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.486123975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ありますわ。どりきゅんに勝つためにやるべきこと……\nそれは、新曲を作ることです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is. What we need to do to beat DoriKyun…\nis… to make a new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.486123975,
      "endTime": 42.4948120277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6337236404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私達五人の想いを詰め込んだ\n今の月ストにふさわしい新曲を作るのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make a new song worthy of the current Moon Tempest‚\nfilled with the feelings of the five of us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6337236404,
      "endTime": 49.7029754638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9096419016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの想いを込めた新曲かぁ……\nそれ、ナイスアイデアだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new song filled with everyone’s feelings…\nThat’s a nice idea!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9096419016,
      "endTime": 56.0968069872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.2677819569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、今から始めて間に合うでしょうか？\n二週間で曲を作るだけでもぎりぎりなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But will we make it in time if we start now?\nEven just making a song in two weeks will be cutting it close…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2677819569,
      "endTime": 64.9230656941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1163987795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "さらにBIG4に対抗出来るレベルまで\nパフォーマンスを仕上げなければいけないんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of that‚ we have to polish our performance\nto a level where we can compete against the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1163987795,
      "endTime": 70.7423851648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.929051717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "難しいかもしれないけど……私は挑戦するべきだと思う\n本気で勝ちたいのなら、やれることは全部やるべきよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be difficult… but I think we should take on the challenge.\nIf we seriously want to win‚ we should do everything we can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.929051717,
      "endTime": 81.4632240297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.678167057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの強さは知っているでしょう？\nそこまでやらなければ勝てない相手なのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know how strong DoriKyun is‚ right?\nThey’re opponents that we can’t beat unless we go that far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.678167057,
      "endTime": 87.7461945059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9038360596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、みんなで力を合わせればきっと間に合うよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll be okay! If we all work together‚ we’ll definitely make it in time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9038360596,
      "endTime": 92.86771354679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.07438008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね\n私もみんなと一緒に、やれる所までやってみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nI want to try to go as far as I can with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.07438008,
      "endTime": 98.27413078949999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.4674640179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……仕方ありませんね\nそうと決まれば、やるからには妥協しません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It can’t be helped.\nIf that’s what we’ve decided on‚ I won’t compromise when we do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4674640179,
      "endTime": 104.26410803799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4574412187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "最高のステージになるように\n一緒に作り上げていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s work together\nto make it the best stage possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4574412187,
      "endTime": 108.7275544961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9142211914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9142211914,
      "endTime": 111.29841609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4984161019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃？　何がおかしいんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono? What’s so funny!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4984161019,
      "endTime": 114.81707831620001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.01041164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ちょっと……以前サニピがスリクスと対戦した時\n同じようなことがあったのを思い出したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s just… I remembered something similar\nthat happened when Sunny Peace faced off against IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.01041164,
      "endTime": 123.8320674899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0566248219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、さくら達が急に新曲を作るって言い出して\n{user}さんを困らせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ Sakura and the others suddenly said they wanted to make a new song‚\nand made things difficult for {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0566248219,
      "endTime": 131.19442559910001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "その場に居合わせた私も、無茶だ、時間がなさ過ぎる\n間に合う訳ないって反対したわ",
